                                <div class="accordion__body">
                                    <p>
                                        <?= translator('A beautiful smile cannot be achieved with white teeth alone. It is almost a visual feast where factors such as lips, gums, smile line and face form are compatible with each other as much as possible. Therefore, these factors are also taken into account when designing the smile, and it may even be necessary to make small touches to the lips or gums. It is essential to obtain a final image that complies with aesthetic criteria, but does not spoil the natural image, does not look artificial and is compatible with each other. While the smile design is made in our clinic, the white aesthetics formed by the teeth and the pink aesthetics formed by the gums are evaluated according to certain criteria and the expectations of the patient.','gulus-tasarimi') ?>
