                                <div class="accordion__body">
                                    <p>
                                       <?= translator('The desired smile design is created together with the patient and the treatment group directed by the physician, within the anatomical limits, taking into account the patient`s expectations and wishes.','gulus-tasarimi') ?>
                                    </p>
