                                    <p><?= translator('In order to achieve White aesthetics in smile design, procedures such as laminate veneer (leaf porcelain), full ceramic coating, bonding applications, and whitening applications can be performed. In fact, if appropriate, the procedures can be continued without touching the teeth, with just the wire treatment process. Among these options, maximum aesthetics should be aimed with the least touch of the tooth. However, in line with this goal, it is beneficial not to get away from the natural image as much as possible. Instead of just white teeth, a more dynamic, natural whiteness satisfies us as well as the patient.', 'gulus-tasarimi') ?>
                                    </p>
                                </div><!-- /.accordion-item-body -->
                            </div>
                        </div><!-- /.accordion-item -->
