                                <a class="accordion__title" href="#"><?= translator('What does pink aesthetic mean?','gulus-tasarimi') ?></a>
                            </div><!-- /.accordion-item-header -->
                            <div id="collapse6" class="collapse" data-parent="#accordion">
                                <div class="accordion__body">
                                    <p>
                                        <?= translator('When determining the plan, it is necessary to examine the gums specially. Every person has a unique smile. In some, the gums are more visible or not symmetrical. The aim of aesthetic applications is to find the best fit for the person within certain criteria. In cases where the gums look too much when smiling, are asymmetrical or the teeth are shorter than normal, it is necessary to intervene in the gums. In our clinic, painless and bleeding-free gingival leveling can be performed in a single session.','gulus-tasarimi') ?>

                                    </p>
                                </div><!-- /.accordion-item-body -->
                            </div>
                        </div><!-- /.accordion-item -->
                        <div class="accordion-item">
                            <div class="accordion__header" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapse7">
                                <a class="accordion__title" href="#"><?= translator('In how many sessions is the smile design completed?','gulus-tasarimi') ?>
                                </a>
                            </div><!-- /.accordion-item-header -->
                            <div id="collapse7" class="collapse" data-parent="#accordion">
                                <div class="accordion__body">
                                    <p>
                                        <?= translator('Although it may vary according to the situation of the case, it can take 2-4 sessions. In cases where gingival procedures are required, it may take longer for the smile to take its final form.','gulus-tasarimi') ?>
                                    </p>
                                </div><!-- /.accordion-item-body -->
                            </div>
                        </div><!-- /.accordion-item -->
